PrecisRegulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1112 - QUINCLORAC) by setting limits (Maximum Residue Limits) on residues of the herbicide "QUINCLORAC" that can be detected in or on rice, barley, wheat, eggs, meat and meat-by-products, and in the fat of cattle, goats, hogs, horses, poultry and sheep, and in milk.
